Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Are the cookies okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought. It's swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Were they undamaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.86,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I might just be a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't aware of that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.30,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I write a love letter, I end up putting it in the wrong bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to invade a house, I fall over from hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I play basketball, I get a ball right in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.81,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to hand over some cookies, I fall down the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Dropping the cookies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Like forgetting to put the love letter inside the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There was that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, they {\i1}are{\i0}  smashed into pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And besides they t—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:39.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,They're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,They came out okay, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:46.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame. Let's try harder next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:59.20,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I {\i1}did{\i0}  see them. They were buying things like spring onions and radishes at the supermarket. Are they like, married?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:59.10,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs33\3a&H96&\pos(132.727273,570)}Statement, Witness #1, Year 2 Class C, H-To K-ji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:05.04,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They left the same apartment building together with naughty looks on their faces. {like they just had sex, kinda?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:05.04,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs33\3a&H96&\pos(132.727273,570)}Statement, Witness #2, Year 2 Class C, K-hara M-ya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:10.13,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Also, they were feeding each other homemade cookies saying, "Here, open up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:10.01,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs33\3a&H96&\pos(132.727273,570)}Statement, Witness #3, Year 2 Class C, N-to H-mitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.47,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs33\3a&H96&\pos(132.727273,570)}Statement, Witness #4, Year 2 Class C, K-shii N-nako
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.47,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0015,,{\an8}Really? Are they like that? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:18.01,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minorin. What's up with your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get inside already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:29.57,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"My"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.57,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.83,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is dry...{I dunno either}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Kushieda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.46,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! What, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.68,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.81,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga is my dearest best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:06.65,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Please bestow happiness upon her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kushieda. Are you saying you're—?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.36,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.87,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You must be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura? What're you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.70,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you were together so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.41,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,but now that I think about it, you two fit together so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka! Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You! Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.71,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:35.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,If you make Taiga cry... I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushi... eda...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.86,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:56.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin misunderstood everything because I was intruding at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Your place was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,really cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:10.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I struggled so much with my parents that when I said I wanted to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,they simply gave me that apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they were those kind of parents, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.59,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The cookies were salty, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was frustrated when I found them in pieces, so I ate some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,They were horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you ate all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You even lied about their taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even as a mongrel, your fur will shed if you keep being so nice to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:38.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you also get troubled while thinking about Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:50.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone understand us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:57.67,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're so troubled, why doesn't anyone support us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.85,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's... Everyone's... Everyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.47,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,PISS{\alpha&HFF&}ING ME OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:07.89,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,PISSING {\alpha&HFF&}ME OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,PISSING ME {\alpha&HFF&}OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,PISSING ME OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the Palmtop Tiger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not okay with being that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even mom, even dad, no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Understands me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with me being small?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me a delinquent just because of my appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with us being together in front of everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for having evil-looking eyes!{ffff}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji, isn't this pole tilted now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's not poss—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0}  tilted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,We won, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I will confess to Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.87,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all be over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Your services as a dog will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,As of tomorrow, we're just classmates who live close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.09,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.98,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.53,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we having breakfast really early today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.78,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yacchan likes canned mackerel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.49,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Taiga-chan still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.33,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.63,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.97,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.47,Default,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.84,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu, we're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.71,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,We spread all those weird rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.67,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san got mad at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.93,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,"There's nothing between me and Ryuuji."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:50.10,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Saying you're not a delinquent, making a huge mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.47,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,She really is scary, the Palmtop Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.14,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I said that Takasu isn't as scary as he looks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.73,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,What, when did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.44,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, shouldn't we clean this up real fast?{being liberal here, they're saying something like "We'll be in trouble if we don't clean this up."}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.78,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.11,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Taiga was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:13.04,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm absolutely not going out with Takasu-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.62,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,"So this is all a misunderstanding."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.04,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,She especially wanted me to be aware of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:24.25,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And she had this kind of desperate, serious look about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.55,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But does that mean she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.34,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean she—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.89,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.14,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.97,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What does she think she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to confess to Kitamura today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be worrying about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:45.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,As of tomorrow, we're just classmates who live close to each other.{repeat of above lines, match them}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And that's all there is to it.{repeat of above lines, match them}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"And that's all there is to it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:01.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!{can be omitted, sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I... Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I have feelings... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh... I, uh... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing it right after arriving at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,If things don't turn out well, this will be one hell of a bad day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.52,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:26.19,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get how this conversation will spell out.{he gets the feeling he knows what she's gonna say etc etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.57,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I would like to verify something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.86,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you dating Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's just Minorin misunderstanding things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.79,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.67,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Our houses just happen to be close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with liking him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.13,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you dislike him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:05.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see, Takasu-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji made me delicious fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He cheered me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He even lied to make me feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Being there for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Because Ryuuji was there, because he was supporting me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:29.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara!}Because of that, I'm now capable of standing here like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you, Kitamura-kun!{fade in or something? hi koda}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, you're amazing.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.56,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:47.15,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I think your feelings were properly relayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.32,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall one year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.{can omit the ..., but she's kinda swallowing as she says it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.20,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike that time, you now have this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.66,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,funny-looking face!{yes, he's not really making any good sense here....}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Funny face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:08.17,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when you're around Takasu, you have this funny-looking face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.75,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu's a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:15.68,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,{soshite}And you, thinking of him like you did earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.14,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,makes you a wonderful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I did earlier...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.89,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:29.02,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm relieved you're on such good terms with Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji doesn't have anything to do-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.19,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,My face was looking funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,My feet, what about my feet? Wait, what am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Was I able to tell you I love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.03,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be okay, Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.41,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't understood what I was saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:51.17,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, from now on, I'm sure we'll be great friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm saying, not friends, I was confess—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.59,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.18,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,{atta}Oops, we'll be late for homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.56,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Better hurry up, Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You! D-Did you see all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but I didn't mean to..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Didn't mean to"? You—!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But what're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.67,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't had breakfast, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And did you even eat last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you went to the convenie—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.89,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why? If you do that again, people will start misunderstanding again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you you don't have to do this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{kedo}But I can't leave you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.53,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you it's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.99,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer my dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:05.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:15.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{LOLOLOL VLC SUCKS}Thus, I'm able to be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ais-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Taiga"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:26.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Since the ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast that could equally stand with a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:32.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{sondemotte}And thus, as a dragon, I'll be able to be at your side, tiger.{can either say TIGER, or say taiga and possible have a note about how taiga is tiger.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to how impudent you can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.07,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oww....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, I'm hungry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:50.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?{sound, can be omitted?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{sore to}And we're going to make a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up on Kitamura-kun from just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{sound first here, time after}Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether you're a dog or a dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:06.47,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said you'd be at my side, you better work hard, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did I decide on this too quickly...?{consistent with how he thinks for himself in the novel, kind of weird anime-wise without novel content}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Taiga."
