Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.16,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0008,,Heart-warming girl, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.66,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0008,,Ah, you're Kushieda!
